      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s still in such incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken super good care of it, keeping it spotless and strictly following the service schedule. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without the full showroom price tag, this is definitely the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
