      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 exemplifies mechanical perfection, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system in flawless operational sync. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock, delivering linear power to the rear wheels. Meticulously maintained, the chassis features documented subframe reinforcement and a pristine suspension setup with original bushings and dampers showing zero fatigue. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no clear-coat failure, while the interior remains a time capsule of Nappa leather. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
