    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a benchmark for the 'mint' designation. This single-owner masterpiece has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes. The interior is a sanctuary of preserved luxury; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible wear or bolster compression, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every technological feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate driver-assistance sensors, operates with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous adherence to manufacturer service schedules\u2014all of which are documented in an accompanying comprehensive service binder. Driven exclusively in fair weather and never subjected to road salt, the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is not merely a used car; it is a time-capsule quality vehicle that offers a new-car experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast.",
